<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">考槃</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contson2e3a46236e67">
考槃在涧，硕人之宽。独寐寤言，永矢弗谖。<br />考槃在阿，硕人之薖。独寐寤歌，永矢弗过。<br />考槃在陆，硕人之轴。独寐寤宿，永矢弗告。
</div>
</div>
